Package com.esri.mo2.cs.geod Description

Support for geodetic coordinate conversion and geodetic objects. This package aids the viewing of maps in any coordinate system and provides high-performance geodetic calculations and conversion methods to the developer. This package is self-contained, thus interdependencies to other packages are minimized. The software accesses a known set of geodetic objects that are maintained in a small, portable, localizable file or files. The localization file(s) is also known as the Geodetic Database. The package is extendible in every manner, allowing the developer to add specialized projections, datum transformations, and conversions.
